Rules for emacs starter kit

RULE:  Put new snippet in github directory then link to yasnippets folder
    ~/.emacs.d/yasnippet-ruby-mode/anaf  # GITHUB directory

  Link snippet to snippet in yasnippet's ruby-mode directory
     ~/.emacs.d/yasnippet-0.6.1c/snippets/text-mode/ruby-mode/anaf # YASNIPPET'S RUBY-MODE directory

  Example
    ln -s ~/.emacs.d/yasnippet-ruby-mode/anaf ~/.emacs.d/yasnippet-0.6.1c/snippets/text-mode/ruby-mode/anaf


Rules for

RULE:

    ;; I DON'T THINK THE NEXT IS VALID ANY MORE
    ;; Places to put the ror snippet changes, other erbs etc link to html-mode
    ;; ~/.emacs.d/plugins/yasnippets-rails/rails-snippets/ruby-mode/
    ;; ~/.emacs.d/plugins/yasnippets-rails/rails-snippets/html-mode


Places to put Ruby snippets

    ~/.emacs.d/plugins/yasnippets-rails/rails-snippets/ruby-mode # no groups
    ~/.emacs.d/plugins/yasnippet/snippets/text-mode/ruby-mode   # has groups


# How to move the rails snippets over to current ruby mode install
$ cp ~/addons/yasnippets-rails/rails-snippets/rhtml-mode/* ~/addons/yasnippet-0.6.1c/snippets/text-mode/html-mode/
$ cp -r ~/addons/yasnippets-rails/rails-snippets/rhtml-mode ~/addons/yasnippet-0.6.1c/snippets/text-mode
$ cp ~/addons/yasnippets-rails/rails-snippets/ruby-mode/* ~/addons/yasnippet-0.6.1c/snippets/text-mode/ruby-mode/


